        <h1 class="title" itemprop="headline">Christian Siriano&rsquo;s perfect fit</h1>

		
    </header><div class="article-image" itemprop="image">
                <figure class="image gallery related-gallery"><a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/pictures/christian-siriano-red-carpet-looks/" target="_blank" data-invalid-url-rewritten-http="">                        <span class="img "><img src="https://cbsnews1.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2017/02/25/6ff7e586-7513-4684-889c-28be1ead0804/thumbnail/620x350/e7bcaa0538f4159edb11de0db6959efe/christian-siriano-interview-620.jpg#" alt=" " height="350" width="620" srcset="https://cbsnews1.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2017/02/25/6ff7e586-7513-4684-889c-28be1ead0804/thumbnail/620x350/e7bcaa0538f4159edb11de0db6959efe/christian-siriano-interview-620.jpg 1x, https://cbsnews3.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2017/02/25/6ff7e586-7513-4684-889c-28be1ead0804/thumbnail/1240x700/9e936f8a9ef8611ad2ad9fae9525d727/christian-siriano-interview-620.jpg 2x"></span>
